Package: violoop-rknn
Version: 2.3.2
Architecture: armhf
Maintainer: Alex <alexliu@zcdigitalsglobal.com>
Depends: libc6
Description: Rockchip RKNN runtime and NPU server
 Prebuilt runtime library (librknnrt.so), headers, and the rknn_server
 NPU proxy daemon for Rockchip platforms (RK3588/RK3576/RK3562/RV1126B).
 rknn_server is installed as a systemd service (rknn-server.service)
 and started automatically.
